RAWALPINDI, Jul 29 (APP):A terrorists fire raid on security forces across from border post in Bajur had martyred a soldier of Pakistan Army on Wednesday.
In consequence of the skirmish, Lance Naik Sami Ullah had embraced Shahadat (martyrdom), said Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR) press release.
